  "body": "Concurrent `client.Pull` of the same image may return error `failed to prepare extraction layer:  snapshot already exists`.\r\n\r\nThis is caused by a known race. Need to address [TODO](https://github.com/containerd/containerd/blob/c45dae71db3337f4f23aa74a98fa2f341aa834c9/rootfs/apply.go#L29) to fix this.\r\n\r\nTo help prioritize:\r\nThis is not super urgent for us now, because we only pull image sequentially in production for the sake of some docker concurrent image pulling issue. However, we may want to enable concurrent image pulling in the future, if containerd image pulling is reliable.",
